    <p>Q Which team or per­son­al­ity has been an in­spi­ra­tion?</p>
    <p>A Re­cently, I’ve been im­pressed with the foot­ball Yoko­hama F. Mari­nos play un­der Ange Postecoglu when they won the J1 League last sea­son.</p>
    <p>Q If you could coach any player, who would it be?</p>
    <p>A My cur­rent team have given me a lot of joy, so I don’t think about coach­ing any­one else out­side my team.</p>
    <p>Q What’s the weird­est fan re­quest you have re­ceived?</p>
    <p>A Most fans ask for au­to­graphs or we­fies. Thank­fully, I have had no weird re­quests so far.</p>
    <p>Q If you could travel any­where, where would you go?</p>
    <p>A If I am not work­ing, I would be read­ing a novel in my room.</p>
    <p>Q Favourite meal?</p>
    <p>A I’m not fussy about food. Any­thing with kopi-o-kosong peng (iced black cof­fee without sugar) will do.</p>


